 <para>
  Find HTML versions of most product manuals in your installed system under
  <filename>/usr/share/doc/manual</filename> or in the help centers of your
  desktop. Find the latest documentation updates at
  <link xlink:href="http://www.suse.com/documentation"/>, where you can
  download PDF or HTML versions of the manuals for your product.
 </para>

